Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！ 國子！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.95,0:01:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}美麗之風吹過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.36,0:02:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有人神秘失蹤？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮上的人一個接一個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是現在都傳言「這肯定是天狗干的」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在皆神山這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.79,0:02:21.58,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}松代鎮民間傳說中，大約距今400年前的時候，豐臣秀吉的家臣田丸直昌無視家臣進言，\n在禁止殺生的神聖之地皆神山山頂狩獵。而在他把鷹放出去狩獵獵物的時候，\n當地的大天狗出現，制止了田丸的殺生行為。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.79,0:02:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確有田丸大人在用鷹狩獵的時候 大天狗出現制止他的傳說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.19,0:02:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣的嗎…那為什麼天狗要襲擊人類？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.59,0:02:33.18,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}日本民間傳說天狗會將小孩子帶走，並和他們一起飛遍日本各地名勝，\n其中最有名的就是「天狗小子寅吉」。傳聞他在7歲時被天狗帶走，\n但卻在數年後（1820年）平安無事地回到江戶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.59,0:02:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在江戶時代 有過「天狗小子寅吉」被天狗帶走 卻意外地回來了的記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.58,0:02:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:40.59,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}平田篤胤（1776.6-1843.11），江戶時代後期著名國學家、神道家、思想家、醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國學家平田篤胤還根據寅吉的見聞 寫了一本叫做「仙境異聞」的書呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.90,0:02:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在並不是江戶時代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天狗什麼的簡直就是荒唐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 瑪雅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 天狗到底存不存在 確認一下不就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.17,0:02:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 捕蟲裝備是不太可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:02:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少小天狗的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.55,0:03:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 天狗！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.13,0:03:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子可是老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.58,0:03:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我乖乖地坐好！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.94,0:03:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又和瑪雅在同一個班級了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天狗嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.99,0:03:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 那裡詭異的謠言多得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.98,0:03:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是幽靈或者怪物造成的 還是超自然現象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這之前也是 天狗什麼的都出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都快二十一世紀了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天狗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.44,0:03:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謠言中 它特別在皆神山
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有象山防空洞附近出現得比較多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了 那到底是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.68,0:03:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天狗本來在中國的意思就是「天上的狗」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是流星的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是UFO之類的也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:04:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏鴉天狗的嘴 或許可能是太空船乘員的氧氣罩設備
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道得真是詳細呢 果然還是喜歡超自然…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的任務是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋找「諾查丹瑪斯之鑰」 阻止預言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那如果天狗是外星人的先行部隊什麼的話又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 也有可能和「諾查丹瑪斯之鑰」有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.83,0:04:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就算覺得很荒唐 也不能不分青紅皂白地否定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果覺得可疑的話就馬上給我去調查
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這些東西給我用你那破手機拍下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.43,0:04:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 天狗的真身是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸或許就是被那殺掉的也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安倍老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.36,0:04:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領帶歪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:04:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.97,0:05:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,褲子的褶痕也請整理好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來教師就必須作為學生的榜樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服裝不整 精神狀態也肯定不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.07,0:05:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像頻繁出入校長室的樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找校長有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個髮型 非常適合你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讚美這個髮型的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生們說 趕快像那首歌一樣 搞成糰子兄弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛上你了 安倍老師～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她交往的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.77,0:06:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安倍先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.24,0:06:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請做好垃圾分類
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好好看說明小冊子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可燃垃圾是週一週三和週五
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分類垃圾是……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次絕對會注意的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:07:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 個個都是這樣 搞毛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看 湯匙被彎曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.75,0:07:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文明君真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彎曲湯匙的內田文明君是也
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是Bunmei 而是Fumiaki
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這個時候的錄像 也真是不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天做的是小文明最喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.36,0:08:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 這不是能回去嘛…！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是內田家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文明 什錦醬菜不能放一旁不吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 請問是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.18,0:09:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.30,0:09:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包租婆？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.15,0:09:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 妹妹那裡的房客嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應 應該是那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.95,0:09:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 稍等一會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等太久…了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太對胃口了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.74,0:10:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太對胃口了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼喜歡吃咖喱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是…已經到了每天吃都不厭的程度吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:50.39,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}看這邊啊 文明君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:52.29,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}弄彎它哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅是彎曲湯匙 大家就那麼賣力地獻慇勤了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…彎曲能力消失的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 能給我一雙筷子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.12,0:11:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 要用筷子來吃咖喱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:11.93,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}文明君好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有媽媽她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會叫我…文明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:20.51,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(1077,978)}Fumiaki
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.18,0:11:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可愛啊 小文明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.18,0:11:23.32,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(1142,978)}Fumiaki
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛 剛才 你說什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.49,0:11:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？我說「你怎麼了」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 再往前一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「要用筷子來吃咖喱嗎」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那麼前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 我說什麼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.63,0:11:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文明 真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:50.63,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(891,983)}Fumiaki
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文明…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:53.47,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(956,978)}Fumiaki
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.93,0:11:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了媽媽以外 第一次有人這麼叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.33,0:12:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 小文明他 不是很可愛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美風 別偷懶了 過來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我知道啦 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實一點也不忙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.63,0:12:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美風小姐嗎…真是個好名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天狗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.18,0:12:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 梢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.30,0:12:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去找天狗了呢 還是去修行了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修行？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.51,0:13:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她偶爾會去站在瀑布下面 或者去寺廟閉關哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 哎…她居然連那些都做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 小文明他 不是很可愛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文明！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調查的事情 怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調查？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天狗的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.51,0:13:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 天狗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.22,0:13:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說天狗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順利 順利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JK？你在找什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天狗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在補習日本妖怪種類
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為它存在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是存在的話 我的探測桿應該會有反應才對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 毫無疑問天狗是存在的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:56.60,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}反應很微弱 很微弱…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.85,0:13:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.74,0:14:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是瓦爾德施泰因學院的新任老師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 是沒錯啦 為什麼會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這個鎮很小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 筷子 筷子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別優待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.90,0:14:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前說過因為工作太忙 還沒有好好地參觀過這個小鎮對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是星期天 我帶你去轉轉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我也很閒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.45,0:14:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約 約好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.12,0:14:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:14:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這車站真是古舊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我的爺爺一個年紀了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.29,0:15:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安倍老師 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.88,0:15:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這是 美風小姐的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 請坐上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊 我從小就很想要這樣的車呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.91,0:15:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還請繫好安全帶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣系的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 伸不進去…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 繫好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先去真田邸 然後去松代古跡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.73,0:15:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 還是說去象山防空洞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.39,0:15:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交給你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:15:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:16:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有美風小姐來介紹…紹～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是真田邸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是古代藩主真田幸教為母親修建的城外御殿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:15.71,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}藩主：藩，即日本古代封地一萬石以上的大名所有的領地及行政機構，藩主即為其統治者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:19.84,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}真田幸教：古代日本松代藩的第九代藩主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼去下一個地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.53,0:16:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是真田寶物館
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面陳列有真田邸內的物品哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松代的地圖 我給您拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.37,0:16:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息日還讓你專門跑一趟 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 順便問問 您要這個有什麼用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不關你事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松代神秘拐帶事件的發生地點 這些就是全部了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.06,0:17:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？像山防空洞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大戰末期 為了把陸軍的大本營和各行政機構轉移至此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而修建的全長約10公里的防空洞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本預定連皇宮也搬移至此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.60,0:17:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 是個強大的power spot啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.60,0:17:20.51,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}power spot：日式英語，指的是充滿靈力容易產生超自然現象的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是松代古跡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 那個不是松代車站嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 這有坐開車過來的必要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐我開的車…你不喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 才沒那樣的事 我毫無疑問很喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 那麼去下一個地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.15,0:17:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這燒餅真好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.02,0:17:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師你那是什麼餡的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茄子醬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:17:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高菜餡也很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要嘗嘗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.46,0:18:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是間 間 間接接吻啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在只是作為點心了 但是稍微早一點的時候還是當成正餐的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.23,0:18:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大米不太容易有收成對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.97,0:18:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以把小麥粉捏起來 然後把醬菜當作裡面的餡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把它放到圍爐的灰裡面烤制而成的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.15,0:18:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的燒餅 上面是沾有灰的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.92,0:18:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 下一個目的地是象山防空洞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 吃東西的時候不要說話哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:18:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師你真是有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.68,0:19:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 這是六十多年前建造的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用心一點 你不是歷史老師嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭結束到今年是54年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 說的沒錯啊 這樣就不能給學生起表率作用了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.67,0:19:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.04,0:19:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 平常都有很多遊客的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.12,0:19:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請小心些 地面上坑坑窪窪的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.67,0:19:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是平常有其他人在的時候 我也不會覺得害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有兩個人的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 有我在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.37,0:20:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 老子現在全身心都要變成這手臂了口牙！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 我都那樣強調讓他幹活了 結果這在搞毛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.99,0:20:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.72,0:20:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 只是看你突然哭起來 被嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.87,0:20:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次看到那些 我就忍不住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那些」指的是…剛才的千紙鶴？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.92,0:20:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些究竟是幹什麼用的呢 有那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.43,0:20:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是祭奠用的千紙鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.81,0:21:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,象山防空洞是個突擊工程 是強迫勞動者們趕造出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.84,0:21:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以有許許多多的人在那裡去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.35,0:21:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到在那種深幽的地下去世會有多麼痛苦 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.90,0:21:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為爺爺那個時代去世的人而傷心 真是個溫柔的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.13,0:22:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待續
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.20,0:23:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿若在疲於應付嚴酷任務的老子的心中吹拂而過的一陣微風
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.70,0:23:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美風小姐真是太棒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.15,0:23:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嚴酷不嚴酷啊 你小子根本就沒在幹活嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.77,0:23:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.68,0:23:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 是蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.75,0:23:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是蝴蝶 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.54,0:23:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.25,0:23:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 怪 怪物…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.62,0:23:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？！難道說它在東京結出了一個繭？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.72,0:24:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.35,0:24:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是太難為情了說不出口…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.90,0:24:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世紀末超自然學院 下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.86,0:24:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文明的崩壞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.43,0:24:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超自然什麼的 太難為情了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------OP----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.40,0:00:44.01,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}十年先の未来が 見える魔法をがあったらな...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:45.68,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}見上げた空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.77,0:00:54.49,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}追いかけ続ける程 逃げてく世界の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:00:59.20,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}悩まずいられるのにな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.65,0:01:04.10,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}時を切り裂くような速さで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.67,0:01:10.83,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}駆け抜けてく　流されてく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:13.98,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}空に揺らねながら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:22.03,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}僕らは飛び立とうとしてんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.40,0:01:26.84,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}さんざん見た未来地図と
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.90,0:01:33.34,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}折れた翼広げ 広げ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.35,0:01:38.87,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}今 始まろとしてんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.25,0:01:43.87,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}誰か呼ぶ声がする
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.15,0:01:53.18,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}暁を染めて　染めて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.40,0:00:44.01,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}要是有魔法能預見十年後的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:45.68,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我仰望天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.77,0:00:54.49,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}在這越是追尋 卻離得越遠的世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:00:59.20,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}本應充滿煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.65,0:01:04.10,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}以仿若切開時間般的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.67,0:01:10.83,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}飛奔而去 順流而下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:13.98,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}即使只能在空中搖擺不定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:22.03,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我們正欲起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.40,0:01:26.84,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}展開早已熟讀的未來地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.90,0:01:33.34,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}和那折斷的羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.35,0:01:38.87,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}現在 一切就要開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.25,0:01:43.87,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}耳中傳來誰人的呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.15,0:01:53.18,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}將那片晨光染盡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------ED----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.55,0:22:20.82,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}君だけのため　光る世界　ここにあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.85,0:22:33.35,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}幼い手で握りしめてた　失くさないよ　ぎゅっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.75,0:22:42.67,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}真っ白な願いを　君と追いかけで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.70,0:22:50.66,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}まだ迷い込む　寂しいげな夜だから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.10,0:22:59.89,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}あの日の面影を　見つけで　思い出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.17,0:23:04.67,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}君がいるから　どこでだって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.03,0:23:08.92,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}何度、転んでも　笑える
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.42,0:23:13.28,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}偶然だとか　必然だとか
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.39,0:23:16.31,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}要らないほど　強く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.48,0:23:25.12,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}きっと輝く　思い出なら　君の側にだけ　あるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.60,0:23:33.54,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}大切な世界　離さないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.55,0:22:20.82,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}僅屬於你的光輝世界 就在此處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.85,0:22:33.35,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}緊握著你幼小的手 牢牢地不讓它溜走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.75,0:22:42.67,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}純白的心願 與你共同追尋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.70,0:22:50.66,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}若是被躊躇包圍 寂寞如水的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.10,0:22:59.89,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}請於記憶深處 再次尋回 那天的音容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.17,0:23:04.67,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}因為有你在旁 不管身在何處
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.03,0:23:08.92,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}即使不斷跌倒 也會笑著面對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.42,0:23:13.28,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}是偶然 還是必然
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.39,0:23:16.31,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我已變得無比堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.48,0:23:25.12,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}若能締造閃耀回憶 必因有你在旁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.60,0:23:33.54,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}最珍貴的世界 兩手緊握 不再鬆開
